data.description: Come check out this beautiful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom single family home in a desirable Cape Coral neighborhood. Open concept, split bedroom floor plan is great for entertaining. Home features wall to wall tile and is practically brand new both inside and out. Electrical outlets replaced throughout (2023) new interior and exterior light fixtures and ceiling fans (2023.) Home features upgraded kitchen appliances. Refrigerator 2018, Range 2021, kitchen sink and disposal 2023. Solar panels installed in 2022 cover 100% of electric services with a transferrable loan .99% interest. Water and Sewer Assessments paid. AC and Roof both new in 2018, Patio foundation in 2022 (with 5-year warranty) and garage door replaced in 2022. Attic insulation new in 2023.   All rooms are spacious. The master suite is large at 15 x 12. The master bathroom features dual sinks, garden tub, large walk in closet and separate water closet. Separate laundry room features new cabinets and shelving. Screened in and covered lanai and large backyard leave plenty of room for a pool
